HEADWORD: Claret
<hw>Clar"et</hw> <pr>(kl⟦acr⟧r"⟦ecr⟧t)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>claret</ets>, <ets>clare</ets>, <ets>clarry</ets>, OF.
